&lt;h2&gt;Performance and Maintainability&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="performance-and-maintainability"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#performance-and-maintainability" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added core benchmarks (including parallel scenarios)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added middleware benchmarks for &lt;code&gt;std/gin/echo/fiber&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduced request-path temporary object creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added &lt;code&gt;RequireFast&lt;/code&gt; path to further reduce allocations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Split large files in &lt;code&gt;authx&lt;/code&gt; for better maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Examples&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="examples"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
